* Understand\nGoverned Tags
** vs. Standard Tags
***_ Predefined keys & allowed values
***_ Only authorized users can assign
***_ Lock icon in Catalog Explorer
** Creating
***_ Catalog → Governance → Governed Tags
***_ Define key + allowed values
***_ Optional description
** Assigning
***_ ALTER ... SET TAGS
***_ Catalog, schema, table, column
** Inheritance
***_ Catalog → Schema (inherits to all objects)
***_ Column tags NOT inherited
** Foundation for ABAC
***_ Tags drive policy enforcement
***_ New tables auto-inherit policies via tags
@endmindmap
